00:03:45.900 --> 00:03:49.020
So we are here, standing
in an empty swimming pool,

00:03:49.020 --> 00:03:51.000
about to try and break the world record

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.020
for elephant's toothpaste.

00:03:52.020 --> 00:03:53.040
You wanna tell the good people

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:55.050
who owns the current world record, Bob?

00:03:55.050 --> 00:03:55.883
- I do.

00:03:55.883 --> 00:03:56.716
- You wanna tell the good people

00:03:56.716 --> 00:03:58.380
who's about to not own
the world record, Bob?

00:03:58.380 --> 00:03:59.958
- Pretty confident, aren't you?

00:03:59.958 --> 00:04:01.410
- (laughs) No, I'm not.
- Mr. Engineer.

00:04:01.410 --> 00:04:03.300
- But if everything goes well,

00:04:03.300 --> 00:04:05.130
we're hoping to quadruple the amount

00:04:05.130 --> 00:04:06.600
of the current record which you hold.

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:08.490
I'm not sure how much of like the trees

00:04:08.490 --> 00:04:10.154
and neighborhood we're
gonna cover in the process.

00:04:10.154 --> 00:04:10.987
(bell dings)

00:04:10.987 --> 00:04:12.450
Only time will tell,

00:04:12.450 --> 00:04:14.430
and chemistry, which I don't understand,

00:04:14.430 --> 00:04:17.133
but we'll see what we can come up with.

00:04:17.133 --> 00:04:19.716
(bright music)

00:04:24.595 --> 00:04:27.120
(bright music)

00:04:27.120 --> 00:04:29.310
We wanted the foam to be
safe to play in afterwards,

00:04:29.310 --> 00:04:32.220
so we used ordinary baking
yeast as our catalyst.

00:04:32.220 --> 00:04:34.110
We could have bought yeast in big buckets,

00:04:34.110 --> 00:04:36.120
but it turned out it
was cheaper to get them

00:04:36.120 --> 00:04:37.380
in one pound bags.

00:04:37.380 --> 00:04:38.766
The only downside to that

00:04:38.766 --> 00:04:43.590
is then you have to cut open
181 pound bags of yeast,

00:04:43.590 --> 00:04:45.637
but that's why we have Science Bob.

00:04:45.637 --> 00:04:46.657
- "Come on out," they said.

00:04:46.657 --> 00:04:48.722
"It'll be fun," they said.

00:04:48.722 --> 00:04:51.389
(bright music)

