to that which we hold dear.

00:07:08.340 --> 00:07:11.460
And so once again, if
this was a total failure,

00:07:11.460 --> 00:07:13.110
it wouldn't be from lack of effort.

00:07:13.110 --> 00:07:15.660
Having said all that, here she is.

00:07:15.660 --> 00:07:18.097
Two, one, go.

